 Drive Peoria, IL 61605  309-671-8411 Fax: 309-671-8480 Quick Links Academic Affairs Student Interest Groups Student Government MD Student Services and Support Office of Student Affairs Leadership and Staff Awards and Scholarships Gold Humanism Honor Society Computing Education About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective Students  Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Event Calendar  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!      If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster   Search for:    © Copyright 2020 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                                  